details.title: Harvey Wallbanger
details.description: Name a cocktail. Everyone guesses an ingredient until someone messes up. Person who messes up, drinks.

details.title: Primark
details.description: Who ever is wearing the same colour shirt/top, drinks

details.title: Big Brother
details.description: Tell the group the last thing you searched up. Refusal is a drink.

details.title: Disappoint the Sailor
details.description: No one curses for a round.

details.title: Humilation
details.description: What is your most embarrassing thing you've done recently? Drink, you are going to need it

details.title: Gym Bro's
details.description: Flex and Drink.

details.title: Shots, Shots, Shots
details.description: Pick someone to take a shot.

details.title: 2 Girls, 1 Cup
details.description: What is the grossest thing you have done. 3 Drinks if you refuse.

details.title: Helen Keller
details.description: Hum a song. First to get it, chooses someone to take a drink.

details.title: Truth be Told
details.description: Say something about yourself. The group guesses if it is true or false. People wrong have to drink.

details.title: Walk of Shame
details.description: Whats your biggest regret. After, drink up.

details.title: Amy Schumer
details.description: Tell a joke. If anyone laughs, they take a drink. If no one laughs, you take 3 drinks.

details.title: Group Therapy
details.description: The group goes around and compliments you. After, take as many drinks as there are people.

details.title: Shut up and Dance
details.description: Do a dance or take a shot.

details.title: Roll Call
details.description: Go around naming everyone's full names. If you mess up, you drink.

details.title: Clockblocked
details.description: What time is it currently? Take as many drinks as the hour hand shows.

details.title: Fox Hunting
details.description: Everyone has to fancy talk for one round. Mess ups are a drink.

details.title: The Great Debate
details.description: Pineapples on pizza? Minority drinks.

details.title: You Come Here Often?
details.description: Use a pickup line on the player before you. If it works, they drink. If not, you drink.
The group goes around revealing their last text. Worst text, drinks.

details.title: Happeniss
details.description: What's the best thing that happened to you this year?

details.title: Glasses Up
details.description: Make a toast, everyone drinks.

details.title: Most Likely
details.description: Play a round of most likely.

details.title: Silence Wench!
details.description: Stay silent for an entire round.

details.title: Thirsty?
details.description: We haven't seen a drink touch your lips in a while. Take a shot.

details.title: Naughty Naughty
details.description: The group comes up with something to send to someone. If you refuse to send, you finish your drink. If you send it, the group finishes their drink.

details.title: Piss Baby
details.description: Suck your thumb for one round.

details.title: Wedding Bells
details.description: Passionately tell the person before you, you love them. Cheers to the happy couple, both of you drink.

details.title: Why would you say that?
details.description: Tell the group your most controversial opinion.

details.title: Monster Munch
details.description: If you have eaten this game, drink up.

details.title: Egg Heads
details.description: Ask the player after you a general knowledge question. If they answer correctly, you drink. If not, they drink.

details.title: No Hablo Ingl√©s
details.description: You cannot speak English for one round.

details.title: Mr Worldwide
details.description: Speak with an accent for one round.

details.title: Twos Company
details.description: Choose someone to drink double for one round.

details.title: Chug Master
details.description: You can yell the word "chug" at any point at the game. Everyone must chug their drink till it's finished. Only to be used once.
